{"tid":1879493,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］想問吓其實做藍店係咪一定要話自己係藍絲？","createTime":"2020-02-14T08:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T09:25:48.000Z","uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f989a1482e3b30333c2c5612a03b19ab566bb090","tid":1879493,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"尋晚同朋友討論成晚 我知係連登嚟講做藍店就一定唔係黃<br />\n但我認為做藍店都唔一定係藍啫 大把人都做緊但佢哋都照去遊行示威 譴責黑警喎<br />\n<br />\n如果照咁講 咁做aco都唔可以話自己係黃啦 政府無能 大家都推行緊罷工罷課 就算你罷工但係你仍然都係返緊政府<br />\n工喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9e277ef815c08e827916a1e485f4d90a5c77a7","tid":1879493,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"其實賺藍店錢 但捐錢比火星 咁都唔值得叫黃咩？"},{"pid":"d24ec08d78f93af42a032d8eb986d3ef7ddf37ab","tid":1879493,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"學術台係咪冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8245c402dae0dbaff307646aa372cf2f5f57fa","tid":1879493,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d8f2feda1a37309dfb13533f256a0925efffa5","tid":1879493,"uid":66999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"喺冇立場嘅公司返工，同事都有藍有黃有中立。老細感覺係暗藍（冇明確表態），上司一個中立一個黃。"}]}